{"title":"夜话","authors":["张田"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":12,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"队上明天放假，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月下拉起闲话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拴娃进城赶集，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问谁捎不捎啥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奶奶要配副眼镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爷爷说买包凉茶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回乡干部要买口新锅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落户工人说捎锄一把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹要一条花手帕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外带一个蝴蝶卡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东院大伯写封信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄给海防前线的志强娃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生画了一幅画，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺便送给报社吧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个要买本《红旗》，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个要本《果树嫁接法》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满院委托满院话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拴娃真应接不暇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知谁在旁插句嘴："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这多事一个人咋办呀？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厨房里走出德柱嫂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗬，这不用你担心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家还有个东庄的她！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拴娃起来把嫂嫂撵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂边跑边说话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“拴娃，今个你要惹了我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹房时，你防着吧！”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}